Field Type Required Description <code>deal_id</code> string No Associated deal ID <code>quote_id</code> string No Associated quote ID <code>metadata</code> object No Arbitrary key-value metadata <pre><code>curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/orders \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "deal_id": "DEMO-A1B2C3D4E5F6",
    "quote_id": "qt-a1b2c3d4e5f6",
    "metadata": {"campaign": "Q2 Brand Awareness"}
  }'
</code></pre> <p>Response:</p> <pre><code>{
  "order_id": "ORD-A1B2C3D4E5F6",
  "status": "draft",
  "audit_log": {"order_id": "ORD-A1B2C3D4E5F6", "transitions": []},
  "deal_id": "DEMO-A1B2C3D4E5F6",
  "quote_id": "qt-a1b2c3d4e5f6",
  "created_at": "2026-04-01T12:00:00Z",
  "metadata": {"campaign": "Q2 Brand Awareness"}
}
</code></pre>
